usage: git mirrortags [<options>]

Mirror tags - delete remote tags and push local tags.
Opposite operation: 'git prunetags'.

    -h|--help               display help
    -r|--recursive          visit submodules recursively
    -v|--verbose            display tag mirroring info
    <git-for options>       options for 'git for'
    
example:
    git mirrortags           # mirror tags in startup module only
    git mirrortags -r        # mirror tags recursively
